Description: DPO1_THEAQ - Also known as pol1. Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. From Thermus aquaticus. Used in the PCR method because of its high thermostability. Has a relatively high error rate because it lacks exonuclease proofreading functionality.
